snippet.title: Dreams of Ylina - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the indie game Dreams of Ylina!
Adventure/Action/RPG.
Steam page: http://pangoweb.com/ylinasteam

Ann awakes on the island of Ylina. No one has ever seen her and she doesn't remember anything. Yet, Ylina is the last piece of land on Earth...

Explore the island of Ylina and find out about Ann's past in this adventure/action/RPG!

Music by (me) Phonochrome Prod. (http://phonochrome.fr)
